---
title: Southwest Beef Tenderloin Tacos with Pico de Gallo & Spiced Crema
description: We firmly believe the week just isn’t complete without a taco night. If you’re on board, you’re in luck! This week’s 20-minute spin pairs sautéed bell pepper and onion with juicy seasoned steak in steamy-soft tortillas. Tasty fixins are a must, so you’ll top your tacos with fresh homemade pico de gallo, luscious Southwest-spiced crema and Monterey Jack cheese, plus fresh lime wedges if you need a squeeze (and really, who doesn’t?).
